ppak.cret.weather

Class WeatherArchive

  • java.lang.Object
    • ppak.cret.weather.WeatherArchive

  • public class WeatherArchive
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores data used in communication with database. SQLConnector uses this class to retrieve data from database, which can be later shown on charts
    See Also:
    SQLConnector
